==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: hayseed
<hw>hay"seed</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>a rural,
unsophisticated person; also used in an extended sense for one who is
not very intelligent or uninterested in culture.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> yokel, rube, hick, yahoo, bumpkin,
chawbacon.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Seed from grass, especially that which falls out of
hay.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Haystack</ent>⟦br⟧
